Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class WorkLoadTest

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.WorkLoadTest
class WorkLoadTest extends Object
JUnit tests for the WorkLoad.java class. This version creates a temporary file programmatically before each test and deletes it afterwards. This allows testing without modifying the WorkLoad source code and without relying on a pre-existing file.

      @Test @Timeout(value=100L, unit=MILLISECONDS) void testWorkloadWithNoFlows() throws IOException
